Name: Final Warrior Quest
About the game: Final Warrior quest is a parody JRPG. Developed entirely in Japan, thus making it a true Japanese Role-Playing Game. Recognizing the inherent foibles of the genre, Final Warrior Quest has tried to mitigate the annoyances while utilizing a humorous tone. Features: turn-based RPG combat system 4-7 hours of gameplay original music that fits the style of 80s-90s JRPGs comedic fantasy setting weapon & armor crafting near-meaningless class system random encounter toggle XBox 360 controller compatible
